\s Kisima cha lehi kingali
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Kisima cha lehi kingali kwa kila aliye na kiu. Kinatoa maji mazima yaliyo ya kuburudisha. \bd*
\pc \bdit Kisima chema cha maji safi hakikauki hata milele. Ni heri yangu, napumzika, na roho yangu inatulia. \bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ulie na kiu rohoni, ukinyong’onyea njiani, tazama kisima jangwani kilicho na afya, uzima! \bd*
\pc \bdit Kisima chema cha maji safi hakikauki hata milele. Ni heri yangu, napumzika, na roho yangu inatulia. \bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Mtungi ukiwa mtupu, ukipungukiwa imani, ufike kisima cha maji yabubujikayo daima! \bd*
\pc \bdit Kisima chema cha maji safi hakikauki hata milele. Ni heri yangu, napumzika, na roho yangu inatulia. \bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Na penye kisima cha lehi upange na kupumzika! Uketi kivulini mwake, na moyo utaburudishwa! \bd*
\pc \bdit Kisima chema cha maji safi hakikauki hata milele. Ni heri yangu, napumzika, na roho yangu inatulia. \bdit*
